{"tid":2110832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Bill Gates 遊說國會加強打擊疫情 稱川普不適合領導美國","createTime":"2020-07-16T07:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T12:59:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6dfbfc55f0a1915041e7b05c62a9f484cdb3b0db","tid":2110832,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）<br />\n全球大流行，美國災情慘重，微軟創辦人比爾蓋茲（Bill Gates）和妻子梅琳達（Melinda Gates）正遊說美國國會，希望它們能採取更強力的行動來打擊疫情，梅琳達更批川普政府「反科學」，批評川普決定退出世界衛生組織（WHO）的決定，認為川普不適合領導這個國家。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n梅琳達表示，他們和布希（Bush）政府、歐巴馬（Obama）政府進行了極為有效的合作，夫婦倆願意和兩黨合作。但他們相信川普政府目前不適合領導這個國家，這點促使他們公開表態。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n另外，她也批評川普決定退出WHO的決定，蓋茲夫婦是該組織第2大捐贈者，她說，沒有人能彌補美國退出後的資金缺口，但幸運的是，退出需要1年多的時間，而美國將在秋天大選，選後會發生什麼？我們將拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3230419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230419&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2bd68430\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230419&h=c5206d2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3230419</a>"},{"pid":"9c36900c2c26a3971b75bc4f3935330f3aa9fb3f","tid":2110832,"uid":121146,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"印像中Bill Gates從來都唔係幾愛美國  捐錢從來冇美國份  而家走黎忽然愛國  咁撚搞笑既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7fcb7214ca1ab85d2d11a8340e208de9a67a84","tid":2110832,"uid":3149,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:57:19.000Z","msg":"美國廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73994349f84e6003481170c72fbd8164c198accd","tid":2110832,"uid":103981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"